Thus I'd mark misleading: yes, due to unclear encoding (axis label mismatch) and incorrect reading of chart. Maybe also cherry-picking if they only show certain weeks, but likely not.

Intentional? Hard to know; mislabeling could be accidental. I'd lean unintentional with moderate confidence.
